{"tid":718079,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【不死噴泉】兩周前被否決　政府再要求工務小組審議觀塘音樂噴泉","createTime":"2018-06-26T13:37:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T14:08:44.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4b43cba0f3a8702c401710f7365c9c4c7574e4bc","tid":718079,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T13:37:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%BB%E5%99%B4%E6%B3%89-%E5%85%A9%E5%91%A8%E5%89%8D%E8%A2%AB%E5%90%A6%E6%B1%BA-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%86%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%B7%A5%E5%8B%99%E5%B0%8F%E7%B5%84%E5%AF%A9%E8%AD%B0%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82%E5%99%B4%E6%B3%89/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%2599%25B4%25E6%25B3%2589-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%2589%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2590%25A6%25E6%25B1%25BA-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%25B0%258F%25E7%25B5%2584%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25A1%2598%25E9%259F%25B3%25E6%25A8%2582%25E5%2599%25B4%25E6%25B3%2589%2F&d=aSudrojFQ0lCV3FZcZzkFR4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=d8d549e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E5%2599%25B4%25E6%25B3%2589-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%2589%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2590%25A6%25E6%25B1%25BA-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%25B0%258F%25E7%25B5%2584%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25A1%2598%25E9%259F%25B3%25E6%25A8%2582%25E5%2599%25B4%25E6%25B3%2589%2F&h=5c9e8a81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%BB%E5%99%B4%E6%B3%89-%E5%85%A9%E5%91%A8%E5%89%8D%E8%A2%AB%E5%90%A6%E6%B1%BA-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%86%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%B7%A5%E5%8B%99%E5%B0%8F%E7%B5%84%E5%AF%A9%E8%AD%B0%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82%E5%99%B4%E6%B3%89/</a><br />\n<br />\n政府擬斥資近5,000萬元於觀塘海濱興建音樂噴泉，惟早前立法會財務委員會工務小組在建制派出席人數不足的情況之下，項目意外被否決。政府今日提交文件，要求工務小組再次審議音樂噴泉項目。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>民政事務局今日再向工務小組提交文件，與之前提交的文件幾乎是一模一樣，音樂噴泉的造價仍然維持在4,970萬元，建設費用各分項亦與之前被否決文件的相同。</strong>不過新的文件就特別提及，早前工務小組上有委員建議擴大嬉水區的面積以助推動親水文化，因此政府在今次的文件中修改了音樂噴泉的設計，「將西面約100平方米的表演噴泉改為嬉水區」。<br />\n<br />\n一直反對興建音樂噴泉的「東九龍社區關注組」在FB發文，批評道：「雖然各方面都已經醜態盡現，但個政府睇嚟唔肯罷休，再一次將觀塘噴泉放上工務小組！」<br />\n<br />\n本月11日工務小組就觀塘海濱音樂噴泉，在建制派出席人數不足的情況之下，工程罕有以16票贊成、17票反對遭否決。對於項目被否決，公民黨譚文豪當時呼籲政府不要將議案直接提交財委會審議，否則是不尊重立法會。有建制派議員對結果感到驚訝，表示可惜和遺憾。"},{"pid":"fb801bc34c8e9a7b1a35a779c3105e87e0dbbd53","tid":718079,"uid":144001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T13:38:34.000Z","msg":"係唔係中共禍港風水陣一環？"},{"pid":"f57d69ce6dac8fe87ce67ca4ba11a77d1d17af0f","tid":718079,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T13:38:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6679a281e4c7ca5690dbd06e527767e6fb4723f7","tid":718079,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T13:48:07.000Z","msg":"又嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解咁堅持一定要起 有草地俾人野餐唔好咩 <br />\n起咗又阻定 大風實成面水"},{"pid":"4aa1e0e93cd23e5c01818ffc74e68a317cd89dcc","tid":718079,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6679a281e4c7ca5690dbd06e527767e6fb4723f7","tid":718079,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T13:48:07.000Z","msg":"又嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解咁堅持一定要起 有草地俾人野餐唔好咩 <br />\n起咗又阻定 大風實成面水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T13:52:20.000Z","msg":"我又幾鐘意呢味野。整左會唔會涼啲？<br />\n<br />\n利申 鳩噏"},{"pid":"a79337893729e25573495d3c7eab025ec7255d0a","tid":718079,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T13:53:02.000Z","msg":"Until I win<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"